&CP2K  
  PROGRAM   FIST
  PROJECT   water3
  IOLEVEL   1
  FFTLIB    FFTW
  RUN_TYPE   md
&END

&MD
  ensemble:     nve                    ensemble type (nve,nvt,npt_i,npt_f)
  steps:        100                    total number of steps
  timestep:     .5 fs                  time step [fs]
  temperature:  298.0                   temperature [K]
  restart:      init                   start type (init,pos,posvel)
  constraints   on
  print  files        100
  print  screen       1
&END

&TOPOLOGY
 FORCEFIELD ON
&END

&EWALD
